{"word":"G2396 - ἴδε - íde - id'-eh - Behold","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἴδε</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">íde</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">id'-eh</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Behold</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"இதோ - எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":"See! Behold! Lo!"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Second person singular imperative active of <a href=\"#/G1492 - εἴδω - eídō - i'-do/1492\">G1492</a>; used as interjection to denote <i>surprise</i>; <i>lo!</i>: - behold, lo, see.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}